Fervor changes gradually over time based on these modifiers.
Fervor can be between 0 and 100.
These modifiers are applied once a month.

== Structure ==
modifier_key = { # The key will be used for naming the modifier
	value = script value # How much to change fervor by
	trigger = {} # When this modifier should apply
}
Scope provides the faith as ROOT.

== Triggers and effects ==

- fervor > 10 - Checks current fervor in faith scope

- change_fervor = script value - Changes fervor by given amount
